### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Valid JSON Echo
POST http://localhost:3000/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "test": "data",
  "number": 123,
  "nested": {
    "value": true
  }
}

### Missing Content-Type (Should fail with 415)
POST http://localhost:3000/echo

{
  "test": "data"
}

### Invalid JSON (Should fail with 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{invalid json}

### Large Payload Test (Adjust size as needed)
POST http://localhost:3000/echo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "data": "Add large data here to test 15MB limit"
}
